   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-a" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell him what you heard from April.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>……No wonder you seem a little peculiar. <BR>Do you happen to know the relationship between our world and Lagendia?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-b" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>She told you that Lagendia is a fake world created from Goddess Altea's dream so there are fake duplicates there who look like people in Mistland? And we may lose our bodies if we meet them...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-c" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What do you mean?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>She is not wrong to say that but actually, this world is a duplicate of Lagendia and Lagendia is the original world. That's why some people here look like those in Lagendia.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-d" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>You don't have to be on guard. It just means that there could be two or three people in Lagendia who look just like whom you can find here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-e" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask for the reason.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>I'd like to talk to you a little more but my mind is filled with something else right now. I'm so sorry.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-e" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400486" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-f" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Actually I think my bag was stolen while I was at the <FONT color=#a82424>Cradle of the Abandoned</FONT> sharing some food with the starving children. That area is in the outskirts so it's filled with all kinds of criminals.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-g" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(He's so different from Lagendia's Pero!)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>But I find them pitiful too. They've resorted to bad ways because they have no other way to earn a living. Since I'm at least better off than them, I hope I can work hard and share what I earn.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-h" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you need any help?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Anyway, I need to go and find my bag but I just received a new stock of goods and I need to check the inventory too... So many things are on my plate right now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-2" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Sure thing.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>What a kind-hearted traveller! I'll compensate you enough so please find my bag for me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Please go to the Cradle of the Abandoned. Good luck.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-a" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>You've found my bag! Thank you so much.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
